Given	I'm logged-in with valid credentials
When I select 'Cystic fibrosis' finding from the dropdown in Page 05
And I select 'Quantitative, Eichinger score' radio button in Page 05
And I click on Bronchiectasis/Wall thickening localizer
And I select '< 50% of the area' color picker
And I select 'UL' from 'R' side

When I go to Page 08 of Thoracic MRI
And I select 'Bronchial carcinoma' radio button
Then 'T-stage' dropdown menu is enabled
And 'N-stage' dropdown menu is enabled

When I select 'Quantitative evaluation cystic fibrosis' checkbox
Then 'Score preliminary examination' input field is enabled

When I enter '1' in 'Score preliminary examination' input field
Then 'No change' radio button is automatically selected
